headline: 3 Reasons to Buy FuboTV Stock Like There's No Tomorrow
summary: FuboTV (NYSE: FUBO) just pulled off what can only be described as a coup.  Here are three reasons some investors might want to buy FuboTV stock like there's no tomorrow (and some key issues to monitor if you do buy it).  Disney is going to combine its Hulu service with FuboTV's business.
